---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy - Trion Holdings">
  <!-- Top Banner -->
    <section class="relative flex min-h-[50vh] md:min-h-[70vh] w-full items-center justify-center bg-cover bg-top" style="background-image: url('/document.webp');">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#1A1919]/80 via-[#1A1919]/65 to-[#1A1919]"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl px-4 mb-20 mt-52 text-center text-white">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg sm:text-xl">Effective Date: May 13, 2025</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section Separator -->
    <div>
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 1440 193"><path fill="#e3ba63" d="m0 74.286 987.143 46.19L980 169.048 0 186.667z"/><path fill="#1a1919" d="M0 0h1440v64.286l-221.43 128.571L0 76.191z"/></svg>
    </div>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="my-24 text-base">
        <p>This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>Trion Holdings, LLC</strong> ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and discloses information when you visit our website.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>Our website is a static site and does not directly collect personal information from visitors such as names, email addresses, or contact details through forms or user accounts.</p>
        <p>However, we do use a third-party service, Google Analytics, which collects non-personally identifiable information about your visit.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">2. Google Analytics</h2>
        <p>We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with our website. Google Analytics collects information such as your IP address (anonymized), browser type, operating system, referring website, pages viewed, and time spent on each page.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">3. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device by your web browser. Google Analytics uses cookies to track your activity on our website.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>Since we do not directly collect or store personal information on this static website, the risks associated with a data breach of personal information are significantly minimized.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-1">5. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us: <a href="mailto:info@trionholdings.com" class="text-[#E3BA63] underline">info@trionholdings.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>
</Base>
